The following files under src/boltz_jax/data/ are adapted (with import-path
changes and protein-path pruning) from boltz/src/boltz/data/:
  types.py, const.py, pad.py, mol.py,
  tokenize/tokenizer.py, tokenize/boltz2.py,
  feature/featurizerv2.py, module/inferencev2.py,
  parse/{yaml,fasta,schema,mmcif,pdb}.py, preprocess.py (extracted from main.py),
  _external.py (functions adapted from boltz/src/boltz/model/).

The Boltz-2 model weights and molecule database referenced by this project are
distributed by the Boltz community (https://huggingface.co/boltz-community)
under the MIT License.

Model references:
  Boltz-2 technical report: https://doi.org/10.1101/2025.06.14.659707
  Boltz-1 technical report: https://doi.org/10.1101/2024.11.19.624167
